collectionMetadata.name: Breakdown by Use of SLA Managed Properties
collectionMetadata.description: Overview of the corporate performance of SLA on the breakdown by use of SLA Managed Properties in estimated gross floor area. This dataset is updated annually.

datasetMetadata.name: Breakdown by Use of SLA Managed Properties
datasetMetadata.description: Overview of the estimated gross floor area breakdown by residential, commercial, industrial, social/civic insittution and vacant properties manged by SLA in aggregate form. Vacant properties excludes properties managed by appointed managing agent. These vacant properties could be put up for any listed type of uses when tenanted out. Data is rounded to 1 decimal place.
